* Colton Software PipeDream - Help *

You are seeing this text help file as no browser was
available to display the HTML help file. It may be
helpful to run a browser and then display Help again.

* Online Resources *

Many resources for PipeDream are available online:

The PipeDream Tutorial may be accessed online at
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/docs/pipedream/tutorial/index.html

The PipeDream Reference Guide may be accessed online at
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/docs/pipedream/refguide/index.html

Addenda and Errata to the printed documentation
may be accessed online at
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/pipedream/addenda_and_errata

Updated PipeDream packages and example files,
including those used in the PipeDream Tutorial,
may be obtained from
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/pipedream


