* Support *

PipeDream is now open source and completely free,
so support is a self-help affair.

There is a Google Group colton-software-pipedream
where you may seek help from other users.
Please include files (in a ZIP archive) which
demonstrate any problems.

Google Group website:
http://groups.google.com/group/colton-software-pipedream

Email:
colton-software-pipedream@googlegroups.com


* Release Notes *

The release notes for this version of PipeDream may
be found in the Resource directory. As they are in
HTML format you will need to use a browser.

A fuller release history may be found online:
http://croftnuisk.co.uk/coltsoft/pipedream/pipedream-release-history
